#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:1
msgid "DRD Generation"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:3
msgid ""
"This page covers the implementation of the DRD save flow — from the frontend "
"validation check through XML assembly to Operaton deployment."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:7
msgid "Preconditions"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:9
msgid ""
"DRD generation is only triggered when `isDrdCompatible = true` in the "
"validation result, meaning all variable connections in the chain are exact "
"identifier matches. The frontend gates the \"Save as DRD\" path on this "
"flag. Attempting to call the DRD assembly endpoint with a semantic chain "
"will result in an error from the backend because the "
"`<informationRequirement>` wiring cannot be determined from identifier "
"matches alone."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:13
msgid "XML assembly"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:15
msgid ""
"`POST /v1/chains/export` receives the ordered chain of DMN identifiers and "
"the active endpoint. The backend:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:17
msgid ""
"Fetches the full DMN metadata for each model from TriplyDB (including the "
"original DMN XML if available, otherwise generates a skeleton)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:18
msgid ""
"Identifies the **entry point** — the last DMN in the chain, whose decision "
"is the one that aggregates all upstream inputs. Operaton evaluates the DRD "
"by calling this decision."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:19
msgid ""
"For each adjacent pair in the chain, adds an `<informationRequirement>` "
"element to the downstream DMN's decision:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:21
msgid ""
"<decision id=\"SZW_BijstandsnormInformatie\" name=\"Bijstandsnorm "
"Informatie\">\n"
"  <informationRequirement id=\"req_SVB_to_SZW\">\n"
"    <requiredDecision href=\"#SVB_LeeftijdsInformatie\" />\n"
"  </informationRequirement>\n"
"  <!-- decision table content -->\n"
"</decision>"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:30
msgid ""
"Wraps all decisions in a single `<definitions>` element with a generated DRD "
"identifier prefixed with `dmn1_` (e.g., `dmn1_SZW_BijstandsnormInformatie`)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:32
msgid ""
"The prefix convention (`dmn1_`) is used to distinguish DRD entry-point "
"identifiers from individual DMN identifiers in the `DmnTemplateSelector` "
"dropdown in the BPMN Modeler."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:36
msgid "Operaton deployment"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:38
msgid "After XML assembly, the backend deploys the DRD to Operaton:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:40
msgid ""
"POST {OPERATON_BASE_URL}/deployment/create\n"
"Content-Type: multipart/form-data\n"
"\n"
"deployment-name: {drdName}\n"
"enable-duplicate-filtering: true\n"
"{drdXml file}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:49
msgid ""
"Operaton returns a deployment ID (UUID format). This ID is stored in the "
"template record alongside the DRD entry-point identifier."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:53
msgid "localStorage template schema"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:55
msgid ""
"After successful deployment, the frontend stores the template in "
"localStorage:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:57
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  id: crypto.randomUUID(),\n"
"  name: \"Social Benefits DRD\",\n"
"  description: \"SVB + SZW eligibility chain\",\n"
"  endpoint: \"https://api.open-regels.triply.cc/...\",\n"
"  chain: [\"SVB_LeeftijdsInformatie\", \"SZW_BijstandsnormInformatie\"],\n"
"  type: \"drd\",\n"
"  isDrd: true,\n"
"  drdDeploymentId: \"43c759d6-082b-11f1-a5e9-f68ed60940f5\",\n"
"  drdEntryPointId: \"dmn1_SZW_BijstandsnormInformatie\",\n"
"  drdOriginalChain: [\"SVB_LeeftijdsInformatie\", "
"\"SZW_BijstandsnormInformatie\"]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:72
msgid ""
"`drdEntryPointId` is what gets passed to Operaton at execution time. "
"`drdOriginalChain` is used by the BPMN Modeler's info card to display the "
"composition of the DRD."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:76
msgid "DRD execution path"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:78
msgid "When a DRD template is loaded and executed:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:80
msgid ""
"POST /v1/chains/execute\n"
"{\n"
"  \"chain\": [\"dmn1_SZW_BijstandsnormInformatie\"],  ← single entry point\n"
"  \"inputs\": { \"geboortedatum\": \"1960-01-01\" },\n"
"  \"endpoint\": \"...\",\n"
"  \"isDrd\": true\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:90
msgid ""
"The orchestration service detects `isDrd: true` and skips the sequential "
"loop, issuing a single Operaton call with the DRD entry-point identifier. "
"Operaton resolves all `<informationRequirement>` dependencies internally."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:94
msgid "BPMN Modeler integration"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:96
msgid ""
"`DmnTemplateSelector.tsx` loads DRD templates alongside regular DMNs when a "
"`BusinessRuleTask` is selected:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:98
msgid ""
"const loadOptions = async () => {\n"
"  // Fetch regular DMNs from API\n"
"  const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE_URL}/v1/dmns?endpoint=${endpoint}"
"`);\n"
"  const dmnArray = data.data.dmns;\n"
"\n"
"  // Load local DRD templates\n"
"  const userTemplates = getUserTemplates(endpoint);\n"
"  const drdOptions = userTemplates\n"
"    .filter(t => t.isDrd && t.drdEntryPointId)\n"
"    .map(t => ({\n"
"      identifier: t.drdEntryPointId,\n"
"      title: `${t.name} (DRD)`,\n"
"      isDrd: true,\n"
"      originalChain: t.drdOriginalChain,\n"
"    }));\n"
"\n"
"  setOptions({ drds: drdOptions, dmns: dmnArray });\n"
"};"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:119
msgid ""
"Selecting a DRD option sets `camunda:decisionRef` to the `drdEntryPointId`. "
"Operaton uses this to look up and evaluate the deployed DRD."
msgstr ""
